 1. I got #cannes awards for a short film I direct  #fallininginloveInbrokenenglish. 
It's an honor to receive this from #cannes Thank you so so much! can't wait to shoot my full future film. 
 2. @dantebasco and I legally got married, we got our license today, and our courthouse ceremony. 
We left the house this morning and just thought that we are gonna get registered, but the universe says “You are gonna say I Do’ TODAY!” so we did it! 8.2.2023 
We got married at the Beverly Hills courthouse. 
I don't even know how to express myself, my heart is full of joy and excitement. 
Can't wait for our beautiful future. ❤️

On this last day of 2023, I want to express my gratitude and love to you all.

As a family, your unconditional love reflects who I am and reminds me of my essence.

As friends, your unwavering support empowers me to navigate through challenging times.

2023 taught me to prioritize self-love and self-care, enabling me to be there for my loved ones when they need me.

So much has happened and changed in 2023. I got engaged and reunited with my parents in China after a 10-year separation. The short film I directed received numerous awards and recognitions. I performed my first-ever surgery. I returned to China and got married in Dali city, Yunnan Province, where I shot my first film in 2010.

I am thrilled and eagerly anticipating what the Year of the Dragon 🐉 will bring in 2024.

Hello, 2024!

Happy New Year 🥰 #2024
